  "guide": {
    "title": "全国大学生电子设计竞赛比赛系统使用说明——超级管理员",
    "content":"<meta name=\"qrichtext\" content=\"1\"><meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\"><style type=\"text/css\"> p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; } </style> <p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><!--StartFragment-->超级管理员账号由开发者生成，没有注册入口。</p> <p style=\" margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:x-large; font-weight:600;\">一、赛事管理</span></p> <ol style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;\"><li style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">创建比赛：右上角点击创建比赛，填写比赛相关信息即可。比赛时间可精确到小时。</li></ol> <p style=\" margin-top:14px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:large; font-weight:600;\">右侧操作下拉栏：</span></p> <ol style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;\"><li style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">编辑比赛</li> <li style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">修改状态：共有三种状态</li> <p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:1; text-indent:0px;\"><img src=\"http://ofhmxbqy4.bkt.clouddn.com/%E8%B5%9B%E4%BA%8B%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86.jpg\"> + 开启：手动开启，状态置为开启后需要手动关闭。 + 关闭：手动关闭。 + 自动：根据比赛时间，自动开启关闭比赛。</p> <li style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">查看题目：可跳转到相应比赛的题目管理页面。</li> <li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">发布成绩：输入超级管理员密码，可以更改成绩状态。将成绩公布状态设置为<span style=\" font-family:'monospace';\">已公布</span>后，学校管理员和参赛队伍才能查看成绩。</li> <li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">删除竞赛。</li></ol> <p style=\" margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:x-large; font-weight:600;\">二、竞赛题目管理</span></p> <p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><img src=\"http://ofhmxbqy4.bkt.clouddn.com/%E9%A2%98%E7%9B%AE%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86.jpg\"></p> <ol style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;\"><li style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">选择竞赛：左上角选择竞赛。</li> <li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">添加题目：右上角点击添加题目，填写题目的相关信息。附件上传仅支持pdf格式，上传过后，参赛者在选题时能够在线预览或下载pdf。若不上传，则这两项功能为空。</li></ol> <p style=\" margin-top:14px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:large; font-weight:600;\">右侧下拉栏：</span></p> <ol style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;\"><li style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">编辑题目</li> <li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">附件预览：在线预览pdf</li> <li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">附件下载：下载pdf</li> <li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">删除题目 </li></ol> <p style=\" margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:x-large; font-weight:600;\">三、学校管理</span></p> <ol style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;\"><li style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">添加单个学校：左上角<span style=\" font-family:'monospace';\">添加单个学校</span>，填入学校基本信息以及负责人信息。</li> <li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">批量导入学校：先<span style=\" font-family:'monospace';\">获取导入模板</span>，正确填写后，点击<span style=\" font-family:'monospace';\">导入Excel</span>上传即可。可能的错误原因：<span style=\" font-weight:600;\">该学校已经存在</span></li></ol> <p style=\" margin-top:14px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:large; font-weight:600;\">右侧下拉栏：</span></p> <ol style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;\"><li style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">编辑学校：修改学校信息。</li> <li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">查看管理：查看学校管理员信息。</li> <li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">删除学校</li></ol> <p style=\" margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:x-large; font-weight:600;\">四、学校管理员管理</span></p> <ol style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;\"><li style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">左上角下拉栏：选择学校，根据学校名称显示学校管理员。</li> <li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">生成账号：填写相应信息，添加新的学校管理员。</li></ol> <p style=\" margin-top:14px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:large; font-weight:600;\">右侧下拉栏</span></p> <ol style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;\"><li style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">编辑</li> <li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">删除</li></ol> <p style=\" margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:x-large; font-weight:600;\">五、队伍报名审核</span></p> <p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><img src=\"http://ofhmxbqy4.bkt.clouddn.com/%E9%98%9F%E4%BC%8D%E6%8A%A5%E5%90%8D%E5%AE%A1%E6%A0%B8.jpg\"></p> <ol style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;\"><li style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">左上角下拉栏：选择比赛</li> <li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">可根据报名状态和学校筛选比赛队伍。</li> <li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">批量审核：队伍编号前选中队伍，点击<span style=\" font-family:'monospace';\">批量审核</span>，即可批量通过队伍审核。（注：无法实现批量取消队伍审核）</li></ol> <p style=\" margin-top:14px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:large; font-weight:600;\">右侧下拉栏</span></p> <ol style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;\"><li style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">编辑队伍</li> <li style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">审核队伍</li> <ul style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 2;\"><li style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">未审核：学生提交审核申请后的最初状态，此时管理员未经过操作。</li> <li style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">已通过：管理员审核队伍信息，无误后确认通过。状态置为已通过后，学生将无法修改队伍信息，只能通过管理员修改。</li></ul> <li style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">删除队伍</li></ol> <p style=\" margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:x-large; font-weight:600;\">六、赛事成绩录入</span></p> <p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><img src=\"http://ou5vc0983.bkt.clouddn.com/%E8%B5%9B%E4%BA%8B%E6%88%90%E7%BB%A9%E5%BD%95%E5%85%A5.jpg\"></p> <ol style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;\"><li style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">左上角下拉栏：选择比赛</li> <li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">可根据学校筛选队伍。</li> <li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">修改竞赛公布状态：输入超级管理员密码，可以更改成绩状态。将成绩公布状态设置为<span style=\" font-family:'monospace';\">已公布</span>后，学校管理员和参赛队伍才能查看成绩。</li> <li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">导入赛事成绩：点击<span style=\" font-family:'monospace';\">获取导入模板</span>，人工填写相应比赛的赛事结果后，点击<span style=\" font-family:'monospace';\">导入Excel</span>上传修改后的Excel。</li> <li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">编辑：点击<span style=\" font-family:'monospace';\">编辑</span>，单个修改赛事成绩。</li></ol> <p style=\" margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:x-large; font-weight:600;\">七、所有参赛记录</span></p> <ol style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;\"><li style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">左上角下拉栏：选择比赛</li> <li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">可根据学校、报名状态筛选队伍。</li></ol> <p style=\" margin-top:14px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:large; font-weight:600;\">右侧下拉栏</span></p> <ol style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;\"><li style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">编辑：编辑队伍信息</li> <li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">删除</li></ol> <p style=\" margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:x-large; font-weight:600;\">八、新闻管理</span></p> <ol style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;\"><li style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">发布新闻：文本编辑器的使用另出文档</li></ol> <p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:1; text-indent:0px;\"><img src=\"http://ou5vc0983.bkt.clouddn.com/%E6%96%B0%E9%97%BB%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86.jpg\"></p> <p style=\" margin-top:14px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:large; font-weight:600;\">右侧下拉栏</span></p> <ol style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; -qt-list-indent: 1;\"><li style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">编辑</li> <li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">预览</li> <li style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">删除</li></ol> <p style=\" margin-top:16px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:x-large; font-weight:600;\">九、通知管理</span></p> <p style=\" margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">基本功能与新闻管理相同。 <!--EndFragment--></p>"
